data.description: Prepare to be enchanted by this charming residence nestled in an established neighborhood. This delightful 2 bedroom, 2-bath home boasts 1,268 square feet of tasteful open layout. The layout seamlessly connects the den to the kitchen creating a harmonious flow that fosters an atmosphere of comfort and togetherness. In 2017 the exterior of this lovely home received fresh new vinyl siding and a new roof giving it an eye-catching appearance but also long-lasting quality and durability. The back of this home has Double-gated fencing to enclose and secure outdoor enjoyment. The backyard features include a nice backyard swing, a wired garage and/or workshop area with roll-up door and  built in dog kennel, a cozy covered attached patio and a nice area to place a fire pit and watch the stars at night. Easy to Show!
